<body><div class=WordSection1>
<div class="brand">📚 ENGLISH CODING · 영어코딩</div>
<h1>🏃 RB001 Week 8 — English Worksheet (Beginner)</h1>
<p><strong>Topic:</strong> Ship It — Publish &amp; Present · <strong>Course:</strong> Obby Architect · <strong>Level:</strong> Beginner · <strong>Time:</strong> about 30 minutes</p>
<p>This week you <strong>ship</strong> your obby. In Roblox Studio: <strong>File → Publish to Roblox</strong>, give your game a name and description, and turn on <strong>Public</strong> so friends can play it.</p>
<hr />
<h2>1 · Predict 🔮</h2>
<p>Read the checklist. Circle or write your answer.</p>
<pre><code>Game name:    My Obby
Published:    yes
Public:       OFF (Private)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Your friend clicks your game link. Can your friend play it? Circle one:</strong> yes · no</p>
<p><strong>Why?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<pre><code>Game name:    My Obby
Published:    yes
Public:       ON
</code></pre>
<p><strong>You turn Public ON. Can your friend play it now? Circle one:</strong> yes · no</p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>2 · Find the Difference 🐛</h2>
<p>Each pair shows a clean checklist first, then a broken one. Circle what's different and write one short sentence about the problem.</p>
<p><strong>Pair A</strong> — Friends should be able to find and play the game.</p>
<pre><code>-- clean
Game name:    Super Lava Run
Description:  Jump over lava and win!
Public:       ON
</code></pre>
<pre><code>-- buggy
Game name:    Super Lava Run
Description:  Jump over lava and win!
Public:       OFF (Private)
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What is wrong? What does your friend see?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>Pair B</strong> — New parts only go online when you publish <strong>again</strong>.</p>
<pre><code>-- clean
Built new section in Studio
File → Publish to Roblox again
Friend plays the new section
</code></pre>
<pre><code>-- buggy
Built new section in Studio
(did not publish again)
Friend plays the old game
</code></pre>
<p><strong>What is wrong?</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>3 · Fill the Gap ✏️</h2>
<p>To put your game online, you use this menu. One word is missing. Fill it in using the word bank.</p>
<pre><code>File → ________ to Roblox
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Word bank:</strong> <code>Publish</code> · <code>Print</code> · <code>Play</code></p>
<p><strong>Write the missing word:</strong></p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>4 · Tell Me What You Built 📸</h2>
<p>Now publish your obby: <strong>File → Publish to Roblox</strong>, write a name and a short description, and turn on <strong>Public</strong>. Open your game's page on the Roblox website. When you finish, come back here.</p>
<p>Send a photo or video of your game's public page, then tell us about your game. Use these sentence starters — write 2 or 3 sentences.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>My game is called … and in it you …</p>
<p>The hardest bug I fixed was …</p>
<p>Next, I would build …</p>
</blockquote>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h2>5 · Record Your Walkthrough 🎥</h2>
<p>This is your <strong>presentation video</strong>. Take a video on your phone (or a parent's phone) and present your published game. Try to use these words: <strong>publish</strong>, <strong>public</strong>, <strong>bug</strong>.</p>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>Show your game's page and say its name.</li>
<li>Play through one section of your obby.</li>
<li>Tell one bug you fixed and how you fixed it.</li>
</ol>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Write what you will say in your video.</strong> You can read from it while filming.</p>
<p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p><p class="ruled">&nbsp;</p>

<hr />
<h3>Submit ✅</h3>
<p>Send this worksheet + your walkthrough video to teacher on KakaoTalk.</p>
<div class="footer">영어코딩 · <b>english-coding.co.uk</b></div>
</div></body></html>
